track_notes: Tryfan via West Gully.  Then across to Glyder Fawr via Glyder Fach.  Descent via Devils Kitchen to Llyn Idwal.

Refer to text on same track shown for NW-003. Do not advise you go up Tryfan the same way as I did. Advise that if you use this track that you go up the way I came down or thereabouts. Do not follow the wall up - in my estimation there was too much exposure.
